			</div>

			<hr />
			<footer>
				<p><a href="mailto:a.kulbei@gmail.com">Contact us</a> | Developed by &copy; <a href="http://goodenough.herokuapp.com/">Good Enough Production 2013</a></p>
			</footer>
		</div>
